@token = paste_your_jwt_here_after_login

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Stock Explorer - Price History
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock/history?ticker=AAPL&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Stock Explorer - Stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock/stats?ticker=AAPL&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Stock Explorer - Moving Averages
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock/moving-averages?ticker=MSFT&start=2022-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Stock Explorer - Best/Worst Month
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock/best-worst-month?ticker=TSLA&start=2022-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Pattern Finder - Consecutive Green Days
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patterns/green-days?minDays=5&lookbackDays=90

### Pattern Finder - Volume Spike
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patterns/volume-spike?multiplier=2.5&lookbackDays=60

### Pattern Finder - MA Crossover
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patterns/ma-crossover?shortMA=20&longMA=50&lookbackDays=90

### Comparator - Indexed Growth
GET http://localhost:5000/api/compare?tickers=AAPL,MSFT,SPY&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Comparator - Correlation
GET http://localhost:5000/api/compare/correlation?ticker1=AAPL&ticker2=MSFT&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Screener - Filter Stocks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/screener?sector=Technology&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01&minVolume=1000000&minPrice=50&maxPrice=500&minGrowthPct=10

### Screener - Sector Volatility
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sectors/volatility?sector=Technology&start=2023-01-01&end=2024-01-01

### Sectors List
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sectors/list

### AI Explainer (requires JWT)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ai/explain
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "featureType": "green-days",
  "resultData": {
    "count": 4,
    "minDays": 5,
    "lookback": 90,
    "topResults": [
      { "ticker": "NVDA", "streak_len": 8, "streak_end": "2024-01-15" },
      { "ticker": "AAPL", "streak_len": 6, "streak_end": "2024-01-14" }
    ]
  }
}
